Screen Layout:Two health bars at the top of the screen, one for each playerTimer centered between the health barsPlayer names/character names below their respective health barsSpecial meter/power gauge below each health barRound indicator in the top center (Round 1, 2, etc.)Combo counter appears when hits are landedPlayers positioned on a 2D plane with a themed backgroundPlayer Movement:Left/Right: Move horizontally across the stageUp/Jump: Press up to jump straight upUp + Left/Right: Diagonal jump in that directionDown: CrouchDouble tap Left/Right: Dash or runDown + Back: Block standing attacksDown + Back (while crouching): Block low attacksBasic Stage Boundaries:Players cannot move beyond the left and right edges of the screenCamera follows players when they move apartStage may have platforms or different ground levelsPlayers can't fall through the main floorScreen zooms out slightly when players are far apartP1 LifeP2 LifeP1P2
